Secondly, cover the same basic
information as your main presentation,

5
00:00:13.343 --> 00:00:15.692
I'll get on to that in just a minute.

6
00:00:15.692 --> 00:00:20.621
And then at the end, we're gonna ask some
really structured questions in the video,

7
00:00:20.621 --> 00:00:23.372
right, to replace that
what do you think of it?

8
00:00:23.372 --> 00:00:25.710
And we're gonna get on to that
in just a second, all right?

9
00:00:26.820 --> 00:00:30.900
So that video really, really useful tool,
highly recommend it, definitely,

10
00:00:30.900 --> 00:00:31.987
definitely do that.

11
00:00:31.987 --> 00:00:34.719
You can just use something
like Loom to record it,

12
